				</ukm:Metadata><Secondary><Schedules RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Schedule DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4" NumberOfProvisions="40" id="schedule-4" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Number>SCHEDULE 4</Number><TitleBlock><Title>Housing costs element for renters</Title></TitleBlock><ScheduleBody><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/part/4" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/part/4" NumberOfProvisions="10" id="schedule-4-part-4" RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2025-03-21"><Number><Strong>PART 4</Strong></Number><Title>Private rented sector <CommentaryRef Ref="key-e59e40319a4bb7062f02734ffea44ed7"/>...</Title><Pblock DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/part/4/crossheading/further-provisions-about-size-criteria-for-cases-to-which-this-part-applies" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/part/4/crossheading/further-provisions-about-size-criteria-for-cases-to-which-this-part-applies" NumberOfProvisions="4" id="schedule-4-part-4-crossheading-further-provisions-about-size-criteria-for-cases-to-which-this-part-applies" RestrictStartDate="2025-03-21"><Title><Emphasis>Further provisions about size criteria for cases to which this Part applies</Emphasis></Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2013-04-29"><Title>Specified renters entitled to shared accommodation only</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/27" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/27" id="schedule-4-paragraph-27"><Pnumber>27</Pnumber><P1para><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/27/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/27/1" id="schedule-4-paragraph-27-1"><Pnumber>1</Pnumber><P2para><Text>In calculating the amount of a renter's housing costs element under paragraph 22, any specified renter (within the meaning of paragraph 28) is entitled to shared accommodation only.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/27/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/4/paragraph/27/2" id="schedule-4-paragraph-27-2"><Pnumber>2</Pnumber><P2para><Text>“<Term id="term-shared-accommodation">Shared accommodation</Term>” means the category of accommodation specified in paragraph 1(a) of Schedule 1 to the Rent Officers Order 2013.</Text></P2para></P2></P1para></P1></P1group></Pblock></Part></ScheduleBody></Schedule></Schedules></Secondary><Commentaries><Commentary id="key-e59e40319a4bb7062f02734ffea44ed7" Type="F"><Para><Text>Words in Sch. 4 Pt. 4 heading omitted (11.4.2018) by virtue of <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65" id="rnb8sic5-d3e51918a1310" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2018" Number="65" Title="The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018">The Universal Credit (Miscellaneous Amendments, Saving and Transitional Provision) Regulations 2018 (S.I. 2018/65)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e51918a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e51921a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/1/4" SectionRef="regulation-1-4">regs. 1(4)</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e51918a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e51924a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/3/13/d" SectionRef="regulation-3-13-d" Operative="true">3(13)(d)</CitationSubRef> (with <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e51918a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e51927a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2018/65/regulation/8/2" SectionRef="regulation-8-2">reg. 8(2)</CitationSubRef><CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e51918a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e51929a1310" URI="http://www.